<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，妈妈躺在床上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她头疼得厉害，还有点儿发烧，什么也吃不下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弗里斯医生过来看了，说是流感。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比护士。”医生笑着对鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一会儿会送些药来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你给妈妈准备这个单子上的东西——</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她需要牛肉汤、新鲜的水果和白兰地酒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>医生走后，鲍比把单子拿给妈妈看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行啊！”妈妈笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们买不起这些东西，我们很穷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道的，妈妈。”鲍比勉强笑着回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们聚在一起聊了聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈需要这些东西。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎样准备这些东西呢？我们好好儿想办法吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们做了一个计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯和彼得找到一条白布、黑油漆和刷子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比一整晚都和妈妈在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，医生又来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小护士，一切都还好吗？”弗里斯医生在走廊里说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿到白兰地酒和水果了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，但是明天会拿到的。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就好！”医生回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天早上9点15分的火车开出隧道时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生已经准备好向孩子们挥手了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是只有彼得在那里，他没有挥手 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得指着挂在栏杆上的白布，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面用黑色的大字写着：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到车站时请往外看！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多乘客到了车站都往外看了，但什么都没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当火车要离开时，老先生看到菲利斯跑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为赶不上！”她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她快速地从窗口把一封信递到他手里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生坐在座位上，打开信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亲爱的先生（我们不知道您的名字）：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的妈妈生病了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>医生说她需要吃好一点儿的东西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是因为爸爸不在，我们没有钱，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您可以帮帮我们吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们一定会报答您的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、彼得和菲利斯</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>名字下面，他们写了需要的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，帕克斯带着一个大包裹来到他们家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>包裹里有他们需要的东西，还有一些是他们没有要求的：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红酒、两只鸡和一些鲜花，还有一封信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们：这些是给你们妈妈的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她说你们这样做不对，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那就请告诉她我觉得你们做得对！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>能够帮助你们，我很高兴！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下面有老先生的名字，但是认不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们做得对。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然，我们做的是对的！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望妈妈也这么想。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他不是很确定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>